biography inkeri ruuska is a visiting scholar at crgp for the fall 2010 she is from aalto university school of science and technology finland where she works as a senior researcher and project manager of the international research project called large project governance she holds a phd from helsinki university of technology and a master's degree in law from university of helsinki inkeri's present research includes areas such as governance capabilities and knowledge integration in the context of large global projects prior to her phd inkeri has had an extensive career in organizational development and management for 17 years working in the financial sector and management consulting
